snippet.title: Crush Link TD Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Hello! 

Crush Link TD is a tower defense game by 4TEAMGB with new mechanics about online dating in virtual setting.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2636990/Crush_Link_TD/

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.a4TEAMGB.CrushLinkTD 

Please follow the link https://linktr.ee/4teamgb to explore our social media. 

Play, share your experience and comments.

Cheers!
